Class ComputeAgent

java.lang.Object
jade.core.Agent
pl.jade.ComputeAgent
All Implemented Interfaces:
jade.core.TimerListener, jade.util.leap.Serializable, Serializable, Runnable
public class ComputeAgent extends jade.core.Agent
This class is a JADE Agent, it is a "worker" class. It will first register the service computeService TestParrallelAgent will call it then and pass a part of the integration calculus ComputeAgent will calculate its part of the work, then return it to TestParralAgent
